@startuml
title Decorator - Ejemplo 3 - solucion para calculo de precios
left to right direction
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam roundcorner 8
skinparam classAttributeIconSize 0
skinparam class {
  BackgroundColor #F8FAFC
  BorderColor #334155
  ArrowColor #334155
  FontColor #0F172A
}
hide empty members

package "main" #EEF2FF {
  class Main <<cliente>>
}

package "pattern" #ECFDF5 {
  class BasePrice {
    +amount(): double
  }
  interface Price <<interfaz>> {
  }
  abstract class PriceDecorator {
  }
  class ShippingPrice {
    +amount(): double
  }
  class TaxPrice {
    +amount(): double
  }
}

Price <|.. BasePrice
Price <|.. PriceDecorator
PriceDecorator <|-- ShippingPrice
PriceDecorator <|-- TaxPrice
Main ..> BasePrice : ejecuta

note bottom
La implementacion esta concentrada en src/pattern/PatternImplementation.java.
Main solo instancia y ejecuta el caso de uso.
end note
@enduml
